data.name: loadButton.ToolTip
data.value:
Click here to select the folder of images you wish to process.
The fifth image in the folder will be displayed and the Tool's determination of its base, needle, and droplet will be highlighted in red.

data.name: calibrationHelp.ToolTip
data.value:
Adjust the Black/White Calibration value and click "Calibrate" until the droplet is highlighted as blue and the base and needle are highlighted as red.
Increase the value to identify more pixels as part of the experiment. Decrease the value to identify less pixels as part of the experiment.
Recalibration may take a few seconds.
